I"p<h1 id="배열array이란">배열(Array)이란?</h1>

<p>| 0 | 1 | 2 | … | n-2 | n-1 |
|—|—|—|—–|—–|—–|</p>

<p>$$
\uparrow \text{배열의 크기를 줄인다}
$$</p>

<p>| 0 | 1 | 2 | … | n-2 | n-1 | n |
|—|—|—|—–|—–|—–|—|</p>

<p>$$
\downarrow \text{배열의 크기를 늘린다} \</p>

<p>\begin{array}{|l|l|l|l|l|l|l|}
0 &amp; 1 &amp; 2 &amp; … &amp; n-1 &amp; n &amp; n+1
\end{array}
$$</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>0</th>
      <th>1</th>
      <th>2</th>
      <th>…</th>
      <th>n-1</th>
      <th>n</th>
      <th>n+1</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
